imdb.plot outline: A rural comedy where the intrigues caused by the upcoming elections in a small village give rise to a ridiculous war between the mayor and deputy mayor. Unfortunately, they have no clue that their struggle will prove to be in vain at the end of the election day.
imdb.title: Las Fierbinti
plot: A Romanian sitcom with drama in a small village in Muntenia, Fierbinti, renamed _Las Fierbinti_ (qv).

A rural comedy where the intrigues caused by the upcoming elections in a small village give rise to a ridiculous war between the mayor and deputy mayor. Unfortunately, they have no clue that their struggle will prove to be in vain at the end of the election day.::MediaPro Pictures
